               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Gadla Takla Hāymānot “Vita of Takla Haymanot” (fols. 3ra-92vb) &#xD;
                     II) Taʾāmra Takla Hāymānot “Miracles of Takla Haymanot”: 14 miracles (fols.
                     92vb-100vb)&#xD; &#xD; Additio 1; colophon.</summary>
