                        as the scribe in the colophon (hand b). The first scribe (hand a) is
                           unknown,<date>Second half of the 19th century.</date>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; name of the protagonist; name of the
                           donor; incipit of Text I and its subsections; incipit of Text II and its
